</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">      </span><span class="nt">interval</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">30s</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">      </span><span class="nt">baseEjectionTime</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">30s</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="sidecar模式演进">Sidecar模式演进</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>模式</th>
          <th>延迟</th>
          <th>资源占用</th>
          <th>适用场景</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>Sidecar（传统）</td>
          <td>1-2ms</td>
          <td>每Pod一个代理</td>
          <td>通用场景</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Sidecarless（Ambient）</td>
          <td>&lt;1ms</td>
          <td>节点级代理</td>
          <td>大规模集群</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>eBPF</td>
          <td>接近零</td>
          <td>内核态处理</td>
          <td>高性能要求</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<hr>
<h2 id="常见问题与误区">常见问题与误区</h2>
<h3 id="问题1引入service-mesh后延迟增加">问题1：引入Service Mesh后延迟增加</h3>
<p><strong>根因</strong>：流量多经过Sidecar一跳，mTLS增加握手开销
<strong>解决</strong>：Ambient模式减少代理数量，连接池复用，选择性关闭mTLS</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>